Features:

Price Tracking:
- Real-time gold price updates from multiple sources
- Support for various gold types (Antam, Logam Mulia, etc.)
- Price history with charts and trend analysis
- Multiple karat support (24K, 22K, 21K, 18K)

Alerts &amp; Notifications:
- Customizable price alerts for buy/sell targets
- Push notifications when price thresholds are reached
- Price change percentage alerts

Market Data:
- Buy and sell price display
- Price spread calculation
- Daily, weekly, and monthly price change tracking
- Currency conversion support

User Interface:
- Clean and intuitive dashboard
- Dark theme support
- Home screen widget for quick price glance
- Offline last-known price display
